clearmotive.ca.clean_text: clearmotive   Homepage   Marketing   Customer Experience Agency Our services Culture   Careers We help ambitious brands win in fiercely competitive industries. We re a marketing and customer experience agency and we re fanatical about your customers. Because what drives your customers drives your growth. We re a marketing and customer experience agency and we re fanatical about your customers. Because what drives your customers drives your growth. business results that matter. We work to understand your business challenges so we can build a marketing engine that drives awareness, engagement, and conversions you can track back to revenue growth. hidden growth opportunities. We navigate the complexity of customer journeys, masses of data, and turn them into actionable insights that spark breakthrough decisions and wins. We meticulously execute big picture strategy. Our senior leaders shape every project from initial strategy right through to execution, ensuring that we deliver both visionary thinking and measurable impact. Our Services Our research uncovers how your customers think, act, and decide. It fuels everything that follows   from strategy to execution to measurement. Our strategies are built with your customers  motivations at the core  carefully and thoughtfully crafted to support the achievement of your business objectives. Our branding process unites strategy and creativity so every creative decision produces seamless customer experiences across channels. Our team creates meaningful digital experiences and ecosystems. Every touchpoint is crafted to keep your customers engaged and connected to your business. Our strategists, creatives, and digital experts partner closely with you to build integrated marketing ecosystems that deliver business results. View Our Services These logos have stories to tell. For over 15 years, amazing brands have trusted us to deliver. Here s just a glimpse at who s been along for the ride. See Our Work Let s make some noise together. acteam.ca.clean_text: Who We Work With How We Deliver Communications Partner We have been building unique sponsorship programs for over 40 years Work With Us Real success comes when you move beyond the transactional and embrace the fullness of partnership. We d love to show you how.  I worked with the A C team to secure sponsorship for an important City of Toronto initiative, ArtTO, and they went above and beyond, delivering outstanding results during a tough time.. They saw opportunity that no one else saw, and were nimble, and able to work with our culture - and have fun doing it.  Joe Sellors, Manager, Government Relations and Partnerships, FIFA WC2026 Toronto Secretariat  A C was hired to develop a sponsorship program for Union Station in a way that had never been done before. They understood our vision, and knew how to work in a multi-stakeholder environment. The result was a long term, enormous win that resulted in an ROI beyond what we could have imagined and an incredible partner in TD Bank. I d be happy to work with them in the future on any large scale project.  Lawrence Zucker, CEO, Osmington Inc.  A C played a key role in helping Calgary Transit secure new sponsorships, including a first-of-its-kind naming rights agreement with TD Bank and the presenting sponsor for our 2024 New Year s Eve complimentary service. Their strategic work delivered tangible results, and we look forward to continuing the partnership.  Steven Snell, Supervisor, Mobility and Partnerships Program, Calgary Transit Our long-time strategic partner, Cleo Social, is available for all your PR, influencer and digital marketing needs. Feel free to reach out directly through the Contact Us page. Get Our Credentials Please send us your information and we ll send ours. Our goal is to empower the Inspired Entrepreneur with World Class, Award Winning Technology, Proven Strategies, and Step by Step coaching. It is the single most important statement you should consider when deciding to work with us. Although we excel at Marketing, Web Design, Advertising and Research, our superpower is entrepreneurship. We understand the challenges of starting and growing a business. We know how to pivot during downturns and pandemics. We ve experienced the tug of wars with budget, time poverty, staffing and keeping the tax man happy. Everything we do is inspired by a business problem we ve faced. Everything we deliver comes from a solution we created, digitized and successfully executed. When you work with us, you re engaging fellow business owners who see your potential, understand your struggles and come equipped with the knowledge, experience and tools to help you unlock the best versions of yourselves and your company. Book A Free Consultation OUR TRACK RECORD SPEAKS FOR ITSELF Over the past DECADE, StyleLabs has worked with nearly 1000 clients and boasts a success rate of in Google rankings, conversions, and campaign efficacy. But what do results mean? It means first-page rankings more phone calls and leads more visibility and clearly communicating your value proposition. It means creating revenue from new and existing customers. We start by designing a great website for your business. We leverage this hub to publish information on social, email marketing campaigns, ads, and blogs so that people understand who you are, what you do, and why they should work with you. It works for us, it works for hundreds of businesses in our community and it will work for you. FINDING CLARITY IN CHAOS - NOT JUST A WEBSITE and a comprehensive digital ecosystem is a critical component of your organization s success. The websites we build are deliberately architectured through the analysis of millions of data points extrapolated from primary and secondary market research. We take the time to understand how people interface with the web and how they make purchasing decisions. This is then digitized into a stable, highly effective, highly optimizable chassis. This website is your nucleus . Your foundation. We then build a digital marketing ecosystem around it. Why StyleLabs? Because we re not a Web Design Company. We re Business Builders We ve been in business for over 12 years and worked through almost every edge case across a variety of industries. Through our experiences, we have developed a comprehensive system that maximizes client success and minimizes client inertia. Track Record Our success rate is a staggering 92 . After 12 months our average client has an ROI of over 20 1. More than 90  of our clients are on the first page of Google. The best part is that many of our marketing systems have been key contributors to company valuations. Our results speak for themselves. Cutting Edge Technology We spend hundreds of thousands of dollars every year improving our software stack. Each month we introduce new features and modules available to all Samurai subscribers. Recent releases included Proposals, E-learning, Onboarding Manuals   Applicant Tracking . It s not just software  it s a full software stack. Proven Process A Big Mac always tastes like a Big Mac. This can only be achieved through process. During our consultations, we are able. to advise clients on what their finish product will look like, results they can expect and windows for delivery. We have worked very hard to ensure that nobody is left wondering and expectations are always managed. WHAT OUR CLIENTS ARE SAYING We strive to be your full-service marketing partners and ensure complete customer satisfaction. Take a look at what some of our clients have to say about working with the Stylelabs team.
